    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone looking for value. While the engine and transmission are functional and start up without issue, the car does show its age with several minor scratches on the exterior and noticeable wear on the interior upholstery. There are some minor mechanical sounds typical of a high-mileage vehicle, but it remains roadworthy and passed its last inspection. This is a solid choice for practical transportation, though it is not a showroom-quality car.",
