    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of any wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the showroom floor. Non-smoker, no pets, and includes all original keys, window stickers, and manuals.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unrivaled caliber, this specimen remains in impeccable showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and preserved to the most exacting standards, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a truly flawless automotive asset.",
