    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! \ud83d\ude97 This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just left the showroom floor. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, meticulously maintained, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for your next adventure, this is the one! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
