    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in museum-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering razor-sharp throttle response through six individual throttle bodies and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and preventative rod bearing replacement. Every mechanical component operates in perfect synchronicity, from the M-Variable Differential Lock to the pristine suspension kinematics. Finished in factory-fresh paint with zero oxidation and an interior devoid of bolster wear or UV damage, this is a turn-key masterpiece for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
